{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87e53aec70","title":"在中共中央政治局常委会第三十四次会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0e6b4c541a","index":0,"year":1927,"month":7,"day":4,"articleId":"87e53aec70"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6be57919c9","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局常委会第三十四次会议上的讲话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"},{"id":"0c9d603495","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年7月4日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"},{"id":"c067acc77f","type":"paragraph","text":"长沙事件为何键夺唐生智政权。唐生智本欲拉我们反何，但见我们没有力量，遂拉拢何键部下打何，故唐不能打许克祥","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"},{"id":"ba228445d3","type":"paragraph","text":"在国民革命军中有几个师和军反蒋，应促成唐生智和何键分化，拉唐反蒋。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"},{"id":"75b27f6be6","type":"paragraph","text":"三有两策略：（一）改成安抚军合法存在，此条实难办到。（二）","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"},{"id":"9e213e0493","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]本篇一是毛泽东在讨论湖南问题时讲话的一部分；本篇二是毛泽东在讨论联合唐生智反对蒋介石问题时讲话的一部分；本篇三是毛泽东关于省此外尚有两条路：（1）上山，（2）投入军队中去。上山可造成军事势力的基础。不保存武力则将来一到事变我们即无办法","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70"}],"page":{"id":"763a20a8bc","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"87e53aec70","start":41,"end":42}}}},"__N_SSG":true}